cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this software, please cite it as below."
title: "Interview Assistant"
abstract: >-
  A real-time interview copilot CLI built on instant recall from a local
  Markdown knowledge base (BM25 + embedding hybrid RAG), using Whisper
  for STT and shipping reusable AI editor skills for Cursor, Claude Code,
  and Codex. Designed for candidates who prepare answers in advance and
  want millisecond retrieval rather than LLM-generated answers.
